            "author_info": {
                "name": "Shawna Palmer",
                "href": "/profile/Shawna-Palmer-5"
            },
            "answer_text": "I just I don\u2019t have a lot to compare it to, since I haven\u2019t seen much of their other concerts. I do know that just about anyone would be tired giving the kind of performance he did. If you look at how much he was sweating, well, that would certainly take a lot out of a person in their late 30\u2019s. I\u2019m guessing it must have been rather warm at the time. And they were under a great deal of stress to do well at Live Aid. The concert in South Africa hurt their image (even though they clearly did not support apartheid), as did in America the \u201cI Want to be Free\u201d video. Guess I will have to check out some of the concerts they did before I was born and compare. ",
