            },
            "answer_text": "I\u2019m not sure why everyone is overlooking the obvious - he had AIDS. HIV/AIDS can be a very slow progressing disease which can drag out for many years. There is speculation that Freddie was infected some time in the 70\u2019s. He was having fatigue and vocal problems by the time Live Aid happened. I have friends in opera and on Broadway and even when they are healthy they come off stage exhausted. Queen and Freddie gave what is widely considered THE best live performance in rock in front of the biggest audience in the world. It\u2019s a miracle he didn\u2019t collapse onstage. ",
